{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund more research to extend availability of medical cannabis on the NHS",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government to fund more research to help make medical cannabis more freely available on the NHS because I believe many people could benefit from this. Myself I have ADHD etc and I feel it would help my brain focus and many others and also help people with many conditions physical or mental or neurological. It's already a proven medicinal plant and I don\u2019t think people should have to spend a lot of money to get it from private companies.",
        "background": "I want the Government to provide funding to make medical cannabis more available on the NHS than it is at present, for all who need it, in a similar way to other current medications.",
